Operational Status Notes: This is the main teaching and recreational slope built in 1973 and reconstructed in 2004.  In 2014 we replaced the surface of the slope whilst widening it to incorporate some waves / rollers.  We also replaced the drag lift with a new one.
Disability Notes: The slope is situated in a public park and is at the bottom of a steep path.  By prior arrangement persons can be allowed access through the park.
